139
00:12:09,260 --> 00:12:10,760
Aku menyiapkan sarapan.

140
00:12:11,290 --> 00:12:12,470
Keluarlah.

141
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:21,100
Ya, aku harus menjaga kebahagiaan ini,

142
